== ಜುದೀತ್ ಆಚೆಂ ಪುಸ್ತಕ್ ==
'''Book of Judith'''


[[File:Judith with the Head of Holofernes by Cristofano Allori.jpg|thumb|Judith with the Head of Holophernes, by Cristofano Allori, 1613 (Royal Collection, London)]]
[[File:112.Judith and Holofernes.jpg|thumb|left|112.Judith and Holofernes]]
[[File:Judith Beheading Holofernes by Caravaggio.jpg|thumb|Judith Beheading Holofernes by Caravaggio]]
